{"tid":1406001,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩厚德商場m3 sports比店員侮辱睇衫示威者係「喪屍」!","createTime":"2019-08-04T11:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T13:18:30.000Z","uid":43983,"like":148,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"4cb3df569c34f69b5e36a7ddc804504b501b1fed","tid":1406001,"uid":43983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:51:05.000Z","msg":"唔好意思個示威者係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n岩岩參加完合法遊行諗住去買件衫換<br />\n成間鋪得我地兩個<br />\n女店員Letty就因為我地著黑衫就同另一男職員大叫一句「喪屍」<br />\n<br />\n我隨即同佢理論<br />\n我問我地著黑衫入黎點解就要比你鬧<br />\n職員Letty即刻支否以對，話咩我地講咩係佢地自己自由。<br />\n我話而家你地擺明侮罵緊我地，咁你指既喪屍係指咩呀？<br />\n佢講左好耐先話我地講緊電影之麻，唔得咩？<br />\n最後同行友人叫我唔好再同佢拗，比佢勸走左。<br />\n<br />\n之後我朋友媽咪聽到後忍唔住落去同佢對質 佢依舊死撐唔應，但姨姨霸氣太強引到其他示威者入黎屌佢，佢最後淆哂底冇聲出。<br />\n本身拍左片 但姨姨應該唔想比人認出，所以我唔放條片上來了。只能cap條撚樣個樣出黎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E9nFz1V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE9nFz1V.png&h=d92395a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p2t5L8D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp2t5L8D.png&h=67a043c1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A5FLL8E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA5FLL8E.png&h=9ddd2428&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w1kf8m2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw1kf8m2.png&h=8d2ff5ab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sdUTU29.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsdUTU29.png&h=d9a0f424&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝今日姨姨同咁多手足仗義執言，希望大家比藍絲胡亂侮辱攻擊時都可以今日班手足咁齊心幫手。<br />\n最後#光復香港#時代革命"},{"pid":"5ac82aceda771c28d670fc94f0a731060878fead","tid":1406001,"uid":247032,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:52:48.000Z","msg":"要加&ldquo;慎入&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支持屌柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7220e608d5c560a8d549e6269da3e2c14415ba","tid":1406001,"uid":182334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:54:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />tko gateway呢啲柒名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03fe8fb569783e0c8316f28ead3b5b1e3df3fa5f","tid":1406001,"uid":104165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:54:48.000Z","msg":"投訴佢啦"},{"pid":"b050feca9fd6d7c58814e69b0f55e9494092b133","tid":1406001,"uid":43983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:55:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/M3SportsHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FM3SportsHK%2F&d=8tXbBdGphLRwD8DFuLHjuK3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=2a4b9a4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/M3SportsHK/</a><br />\nPage傳送門"},{"pid":"a4aa9831def21b0dbc912663d098395be9ea9ca3","tid":1406001,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"197ba48a8092b7ed29df9396cb47f75cc27f59dc","tid":1406001,"uid":46758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:56:07.000Z","msg":"投訴<br />\n入黎幫襯仲要俾你屌"},{"pid":"edc94224d5d90801ae82b2f41fb98bce0120c603","tid":1406001,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:56:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"048500fc980d9f499b9ca03b37a31b760342ece5","tid":1406001,"uid":69841,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:59:49.000Z","msg":"係時候發揮香港投訴之都嘅精神"},{"pid":"6cf524b19a04efc6a895f589a1884f72725f8f4d","tid":1406001,"uid":238415,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:01:55.000Z","msg":"點解對家絕大部份都係呢d樣？"},{"pid":"b230ac93320d4718ba5e86da